UNITED STATES of America, Appellant, v. John ROBERTSON, Appellee. No. 6929. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 10, 1932.

Before SAWTELLE, Circuit Judge, and KERRIGAN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal herein dismissed; mandate forthwith.
